+   set.seed(0xBEEF)

+   stopifnot(all.equal(y4, y3))

[10:19:27.680]             base::options(...future.oldOptions)
[10:19:27.680]             if (.Platform$OS.type == "windows") {
[10:19:27.680]                 old_names <- names(...future.oldEnvVars)
[10:19:27.680]                 envs <- base::Sys.getenv()
[10:19:27.680]                 names <- names(envs)
[10:19:27.680]                 common <- intersect(names, old_names)
[10:19:27.680]                 added <- setdiff(names, old_names)
[10:19:27.680]                 removed <- setdiff(old_names, names)
[10:19:27.680]                 changed <- common[...future.oldEnvVars[common] != 
[10:19:27.680]                   envs[common]]
[10:19:27.680]                 NAMES <- toupper(changed)
[10:19:27.680]                 args <- list()
[10:19:27.680]                 for (kk in seq_along(NAMES)) {
[10:19:27.680]                   name <- changed[[kk]]
[10:19:27.680]                   NAME <- NAMES[[kk]]
[10:19:27.680]                   if (name != NAME && is.element(NAME, old_names)) 
[10:19:27.680]                     next
[10:19:27.680]                   args[[name]] <- ...future.oldEnvVars[[name]]
[10:19:27.680]                 }
[10:19:27.680]                 NAMES <- toupper(added)
[10:19:27.680]                 for (kk in seq_along(NAMES)) {
[10:19:27.680]                   name <- added[[kk]]
[10:19:27.680]                   NAME <- NAMES[[kk]]
[10:19:27.680]                   if (name != NAME && is.element(NAME, old_names)) 
[10:19:27.680]                     next
[10:19:27.680]                   args[[name]] <- ""
[10:19:27.680]                 }
[10:19:27.680]                 NAMES <- toupper(removed)
[10:19:27.680]                 for (kk in seq_along(NAMES)) {
[10:19:27.680]                   name <- removed[[kk]]
[10:19:27.680]                   NAME <- NAMES[[kk]]
[10:19:27.680]                   if (name != NAME && is.element(NAME, old_names)) 
[10:19:27.680]                     next
[10:19:27.680]                   args[[name]] <- ...future.oldEnvVars[[name]]
[10:19:27.680]                 }
[10:19:27.680]                 if (length(args) > 0) 
[10:19:27.680]                   base::do.call(base::Sys.setenv, args = args)
[10:19:27.680]                 args <- names <- old_names <- NAMES <- envs <- common <- added <- removed <- NULL
[10:19:27.680]             }
[10:19:27.680]             else {
[10:19:27.680]                 base::do.call(base::Sys.setenv, args = base::as.list(...future.oldEnvVars))
[10:19:27.680]             }

[10:19:27.836]                   muffleCondition <- function (cond, pattern = "^muffle") 
[10:19:27.836]                   {
[10:19:27.836]                     inherits <- base::inherits
[10:19:27.836]                     invokeRestart <- base::invokeRestart
[10:19:27.836]                     is.null <- base::is.null
[10:19:27.836]                     muffled <- FALSE
[10:19:27.836]                     if (inherits(cond, "message")) {
[10:19:27.836]                       muffled <- grepl(pattern, "muffleMessage")
[10:19:27.836]                       if (muffled) 
[10:19:27.836]                         invokeRestart("muffleMessage")
[10:19:27.836]                     }
[10:19:27.836]                     else if (inherits(cond, "warning")) {
[10:19:27.836]                       muffled <- grepl(pattern, "muffleWarning")
[10:19:27.836]                       if (muffled) 
[10:19:27.836]                         invokeRestart("muffleWarning")
[10:19:27.836]                     }
[10:19:27.836]                     else if (inherits(cond, "condition")) {
[10:19:27.836]                       if (!is.null(pattern)) {
[10:19:27.836]                         computeRestarts <- base::computeRestarts
[10:19:27.836]                         grepl <- base::grepl
[10:19:27.836]                         restarts <- computeRestarts(cond)
[10:19:27.836]                         for (restart in restarts) {
[10:19:27.836]                           name <- restart$name
[10:19:27.836]                           if (is.null(name)) 
[10:19:27.836]                             next
[10:19:27.836]                           if (!grepl(pattern, name)) 
[10:19:27.836]                             next
[10:19:27.836]                           invokeRestart(restart)
[10:19:27.836]                           muffled <- TRUE
[10:19:27.836]                           break
[10:19:27.836]                         }
[10:19:27.836]                       }
[10:19:27.836]                     }
[10:19:27.836]                     invisible(muffled)
[10:19:27.836]                   }
[10:19:27.836]                   muffleCondition(cond)
[10:19:27.836]                 })
[10:19:27.836]             }))

[10:19:28.189]                 }

[10:19:28.189]                 }
[10:19:28.189]                 NAMES <- toupper(removed)

[10:19:28.189]                 }

[10:19:28.189]                 args <- names <- old_names <- NAMES <- envs <- common <- added <- removed <- NULL
[10:19:28.189]             }

[10:19:28.229]                   save_rds <- function (object, pathname, ...) 
[10:19:28.229]                   {
[10:19:28.229]                     pathname_tmp <- sprintf("%s.tmp", pathname)
[10:19:28.229]                     if (file_test("-f", pathname_tmp)) {
[10:19:28.229]                       fi_tmp <- file.info(pathname_tmp)
[10:19:28.229]                       stopf("Cannot save RDS file because a temporary save file already exists: %s (%0.f bytes; last modified on %s)", 
[10:19:28.229]                         sQuote(pathname_tmp), fi_tmp[["size"]], 
[10:19:28.229]                         fi_tmp[["mtime"]])
[10:19:28.229]                     }

[10:19:28.229]                       saveRDS(object, file = pathname_tmp, ...)
[10:19:28.229]                     }, error = function(ex) {

[10:19:28.229]                       fi_tmp <- file.info(pathname_tmp)
[10:19:28.229]                       msg <- sprintf("saveRDS() failed to save to temporary file %s (%.0f bytes; last modified on %s). The reason was: %s", 
[10:19:28.229]                         sQuote(pathname_tmp), fi_tmp[["size"]], 
[10:19:28.229]                         fi_tmp[["mtime"]], msg)
[10:19:28.229]                       ex$message <- msg
[10:19:28.229]                       stop(ex)
[10:19:28.229]                     })
[10:19:28.229]                     stopifnot(file_test("-f", pathname_tmp))
[10:19:28.229]                     res <- file.rename(from = pathname_tmp, to = pathname)
[10:19:28.229]                     if (!res || file_test("-f", pathname_tmp)) {
[10:19:28.229]                       fi_tmp <- file.info(pathname_tmp)
[10:19:28.229]                       fi <- file.info(pathname)

[10:19:28.229]                         sQuote(pathname_tmp), fi_tmp[["size"]],

[10:19:28.229]                   saveImmediateCondition(cond, path = "/tmp/RtmpfOq40q/.future/immediateConditions")
[10:19:28.229]                   muffleCondition <- function (cond, pattern = "^muffle") 
[10:19:28.229]                   {
[10:19:28.229]                     inherits <- base::inherits
[10:19:28.229]                     invokeRestart <- base::invokeRestart
[10:19:28.229]                     is.null <- base::is.null
[10:19:28.229]                     muffled <- FALSE
[10:19:28.229]                     if (inherits(cond, "message")) {
[10:19:28.229]                       muffled <- grepl(pattern, "muffleMessage")
[10:19:28.229]                       if (muffled) 
[10:19:28.229]                         invokeRestart("muffleMessage")
[10:19:28.229]                     }
[10:19:28.229]                     else if (inherits(cond, "warning")) {
[10:19:28.229]                       muffled <- grepl(pattern, "muffleWarning")
[10:19:28.229]                       if (muffled) 
[10:19:28.229]                         invokeRestart("muffleWarning")
[10:19:28.229]                     }
[10:19:28.229]                     else if (inherits(cond, "condition")) {
[10:19:28.229]                       if (!is.null(pattern)) {
[10:19:28.229]                         computeRestarts <- base::computeRestarts
[10:19:28.229]                         grepl <- base::grepl
[10:19:28.229]                         restarts <- computeRestarts(cond)
[10:19:28.229]                         for (restart in restarts) {
[10:19:28.229]                           name <- restart$name
[10:19:28.229]                           if (is.null(name)) 
[10:19:28.229]                             next
[10:19:28.229]                           if (!grepl(pattern, name)) 
[10:19:28.229]                             next
[10:19:28.229]                           invokeRestart(restart)
[10:19:28.229]                           muffled <- TRUE
[10:19:28.229]                           break
[10:19:28.229]                         }

[10:19:29.616]                 removed <- setdiff(old_names, names)

[10:19:29.878]                         if (muffled) 
[10:19:29.878]                           invokeRestart("muffleWarning")
[10:19:29.878]                       }

[10:19:29.878]                           computeRestarts <- base::computeRestarts
[10:19:29.878]                           grepl <- base::grepl
[10:19:29.878]                           restarts <- computeRestarts(cond)
[10:19:29.878]                           for (restart in restarts) {
[10:19:29.878]                             name <- restart$name
[10:19:29.878]                             if (is.null(name)) 
[10:19:29.878]                               next
[10:19:29.878]                             if (!grepl(pattern, name)) 
[10:19:29.878]                               next
[10:19:29.878]                             invokeRestart(restart)
[10:19:29.878]                             muffled <- TRUE
[10:19:29.878]                             break
[10:19:29.878]                           }
[10:19:29.878]                         }
[10:19:29.878]                       }
[10:19:29.878]                       invisible(muffled)
[10:19:29.878]                     }
[10:19:29.878]                     muffleCondition(cond, pattern = "^muffle")
[10:19:29.878]                   }
[10:19:29.878]                 }
